sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant H as Hermes 3 (Brain)
    participant O as OpenClaw (Body)
    participant E as External SystemU->>H: Request complex task
    H->>H: Recursive Reasoning
    H->>O: Send Action Plan
